{"tid":1395582,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"多謝年輕人，已指示員工8月5日罷工","createTime":"2019-08-01T19:48:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T20:09:43.000Z","uid":273834,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"43ede5db92fa9e38fc176acdbc7388947c8e91d6","tid":1395582,"uid":273834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:48:56.000Z","msg":"本人中小企老細，小康之家，以前多數沉默唖忍政治暴力，感謝前線義士種種勇氣及犧牲，另不少人包括自己覺醒，不可中立，亦想付出多些，捐助良心傳媒，義士基金，物資上前缐，現在也指示公司員工響應罷工，並於社交媒體呼籲，及不要當日外出吃喝玩樂消費，以免助長經濟。<br />\n希望其他老闆也一齊參予，為香港公義自由社會出一分力。<br />\n亦懇請所有以前港人引以為傲的警隊不要再助紂為虐，向爛得一團糟的政府說不。"},{"pid":"e18bc557c0023688c03488266991410c03841515","tid":1395582,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:54:05.000Z","msg":"老闆識ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"409a5df2432f25dcb0b95e2f4849db9f7f91e427","tid":1395582,"uid":67346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:57:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n感謝加入罷工行列"},{"pid":"fa6c82d93855a31ae125841424ece1c533ca9834","tid":1395582,"uid":191309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:58:43.000Z","msg":"ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab77db9276fbb39f089202a44d7b6acf801136d","tid":1395582,"uid":112681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:59:40.000Z","msg":"多謝你"},{"pid":"cb69fc759911ef568d70e4783d6af5522341d274","tid":1395582,"uid":108571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T20:08:07.000Z","msg":"多謝你<br />\n良心公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f3a262979f172a82a861a861ce3799c7c71dbb9","tid":1395582,"uid":23184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T20:09:43.000Z","msg":"良心老闆請唔請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmo